ActPersonal Information Protection and Electronic Documents Act
SubjectPersonal Health Information Custodians in Nova Scotia Exemption Order
PrecisPERSONAL HEALTH INFORMATION CUSTODIANS IN NOVA SCOTIA EXEMPTION ORDER in order to (1) demonstrate the federal government's commitment to ensure that a patchwork of legislation of differing standards does not occur; and (2) signal that custodians of personal health information in Nova Scotia would no longer be subject to Part 1 of the Personal Information Protection and Electronic Documents Act.
